WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.466 --> 00:00:02.533
I wish the Empress Dowager a thousand years.

2
00:00:02.533 --> 00:00:04.333
May the Empress Dowager be blessed abundantly.

3
00:00:04.333 --> 00:00:05.700
May her life be as long as Nanshan.

4
00:00:10.566 --> 00:00:13.400
In the previous life, they poisoned Princess Loulan.

5
00:00:13.800 --> 00:00:16.900
I fear that if Biyuan keeps a close watch and fails,

6
00:00:16.933 --> 00:00:18.166
they will definitely advance another level.

7
00:00:23.733 --> 00:00:25.566
This bird embroidery is really good.

8
00:00:25.733 --> 00:00:28.566
But the phoenix lacks some charm.

9
00:00:28.700 --> 00:00:30.466
Aside from the Empress,

10
00:00:30.466 --> 00:00:31.666
other consorts

11
00:00:31.666 --> 00:00:34.400
do not have the right to be gifted a phoenix in their embroidery.

12
00:00:34.600 --> 00:00:36.700
It’s normal for palace maids to be inexperienced.

13
00:00:36.766 --> 00:00:40.700
In the future, they should focus more on bird and flower patterns.

14
00:00:40.900 --> 00:00:43.566
As for the phoenix, better not to embroider it.

15
00:00:43.666 --> 00:00:46.666
It’s a waste of effort. I will respectfully follow the Empress Dowager's teaching.

16
00:00:55.166 --> 00:00:55.966
Be careful.

17
00:00:57.566 --> 00:00:59.000
Ah!

18
00:01:07.700 --> 00:01:08.500
Ah!

19
00:01:11.766 --> 00:01:12.566
Cai Yi!

20
00:01:14.100 --> 00:01:16.066
Sheng Wo, listen carefully.

21
00:01:16.066 --> 00:01:18.666
You need to investigate today’s incident thoroughly.

22
00:01:18.666 --> 00:01:19.900
All involved parties,

23
00:01:19.966 --> 00:01:21.666
from the Empress Dowager to the palace maids,

24
00:01:21.666 --> 00:01:24.300
interrogate everyone with suspicion.

25
00:01:24.300 --> 00:01:26.400
I give you the authority as if I were present myself.

26
00:01:26.666 --> 00:01:28.866
If you still can’t find the result,

27
00:01:29.066 --> 00:01:31.700
then you and all the wise men will face death.
